                                            <h2 class="ez-toc-section" id="tuliskan-2-contoh-kalimat-yang-menyatakan-pendapat-tentang-wali-kelas-sekolah-kelas-dan-mengenai-jurusan">
                            20. Tuliskan 2 contoh kalimat yang menyatakan pendapat tentang wali kelas, sekolah, kelas dan mengenai jurusan</h2><br />
                        A.) CLASS ADVISOR (HOMEROOM TEACHER)<br />1. My homeroom teacher, Miss Patonah Olivia, is a smart lady. She can teach well.<br />2. Do you know Mr. Juma'in Bon Jovi? He is my homeroom teacher. He is a wise person and loves education.<br /><br />B.) SCHOOL <br />1. Our school, the SMAN Kendal 90, is famous for its soccer sport. You know, we beat Manchester United 6-0. It's not a hoax, even Christian Ronaldo was surprised.<br />2. The best marching band performance in 1908 was won by a vocational school in Juwingan, Surabaya.<br /><br />C.) CLASS<br />1. Look at our class, we have only 15 students. Great for learning process.<br />2. The school board was delighted to see our class. We have famous students like Syahrini, Rizieq, Egypt Sugigi, and Chelsea Steel.<br /><br />D.) SCHOOL MAJORS<br />1. Anniesa Hasibuan, the smart student, choose social studies as her major.<br />2. Sciences &amp; mathematics belong to the science major and it is not easy for your brain, like yours, Jing-min.<br />
